---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Affiliate Disclosure | Ibiza Cool Party',
  description: 'Learn how Ibiza Cool Party earns revenue through affiliate partnerships with ticket platforms, hotels, and transfer services.',
  noindex: true,
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 prose prose-invert">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p>
      Ibiza Cool Party is a participant in several affiliate programs. This means that when you click on certain links on our site and make a purchase or booking, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you.
    </p>
    <h2>Our Partners</h2>
    <p>We work with the following affiliate programs:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Clubtickets</strong> – Club tickets and event entry for Ibiza venues</li>
      <li><strong>Booking.com</strong> – Hotel and accommodation bookings</li>
      <li><strong>GetYourGuide</strong> – Tours, boat parties, and experiences</li>
      <li><strong>Welcome Pickups</strong> – Airport transfers and transportation</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p>
      When you book through our links, the service provider pays us a small commission. This does not affect the price you pay — you pay the same amount as if you'd gone directly to the provider's website.
    </p>
    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
    <p>
      We only recommend services and venues that we genuinely believe will enhance your Ibiza experience. Our editorial content is independent and not influenced by our affiliate relationships.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you have any questions about our affiliate partnerships, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
